Step: `mount`
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mount a filesystem.

Step keys:

* `mount` &mdash; REQUIRED; tag of filesystem to mount.

* `dirname` &mdash; OPTIONAL; the mount point.

* `mount-on` &mdash; OPTIONAL; tag of already mounted filesystem in
  image. (FIXME: this may be wrong?)

Example (in the .vmdb file):

    - mount: root
